<!doctype html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>김민지 | Portfolio</title>
  <meta name="description" content="김민지 포트폴리오 — AI 영상·영화 제작, 콘텐츠 기획/디자인" />

  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />

  <style>
    :root{
      --main:#0018FF;
      --bg:#ffffff;
      --text:#111111;
      --muted:#555;
      --gray:#f5f7fb;
      --card:#ffffff;
      --border:rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
      --shadow:0 10px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
      --radius:28px;
      --container:1120px;
    }

    *{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}
    html{scroll-behavior:smooth}
    body{
      font-family:"Noto Sans KR", system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, sans-serif;
      background:var(--bg);
      color:var(--text);
      line-height:1.7;
      overflow-x:hidden;
    }
    a{color:inherit; text-decoration:none;}
    ul{list-style:none}

    .container{
      width:min(var(--container), 100%);
      margin:0 auto;
      padding:0 10%;
    }

    /* Top nav */
    .topbar{
      position:fixed;
      inset:0 0 auto 0;
      z-index:50;
      padding:14px 0;
      background:rgba(255,255,255,0.65);
      border-bottom:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    }
    .topbar .inner{
      width:min(var(--container), 100%);
      margin:0 auto;
      padding:0 10%;
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      justify-content:space-between;
      gap:14px;
    }
    .brand{
      font-weight:800;
      letter-spacing:-0.02em;
    }
    .nav{
      display:flex;
      gap:16px;
    }
    .nav a{
      font-weight:600;
      font-size:14px;
      color:#222;
      padding:8px 10px;
      border-radius:999px;
    }
    .nav a:hover{
      background:rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
    }

    /* Sections */
    section{padding:120px 0}
    .section-title{
      font-size:44px;
      font-weight:900;
      letter-spacing:-0.03em;
      color:var(--main);
      margin-bottom:18px;
    }
    .section-desc{
      font-size:18px;
      color:var(--muted);
      margin-bottom:56px;
      max-width:820px;
    }

    /* Hero (Center focus) */
    header.hero{
      min-height:100vh;
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      justify-content:center;
      position:relative;
      overflow:hidden;
      background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0018FF 0%,#0f2dff 40%,#ffffff 100%);
      color:#fff;
      text-align:center;
      padding-top:84px;
    }
    header.hero::after{
      content:"";
      position:absolute;
      width:620px;height:620px;
      background:rgba(255,255,255,0.10);
      border-radius:999px;
      right:-220px;top:-160px;
    }
    
    .hero h1{
      font-size:72px;
      font-weight:900;
      line-height:1.08;
      letter-spacing:-0.04em;
      margin-bottom:28px;
    }
    .hero p{
      font-size:20px;
      opacity:0.95;
      max-width:800px;
      margin:0 auto 36px;
    }

    .cta-row{
      display:flex;
      gap:12px;
      justify-content:center;
      flex-wrap:wrap;
    }

    .btn{
      display:inline-flex;
      align-items:center;
      justify-content:center;
      gap:10px;
      padding:16px 28px;
      border-radius:999px;
      font-weight:700;
      transition:0.2s ease;
      border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.28);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    }
    .btn.primary{
      background:#fff;
      color:var(--main);
      border-color:#fff;
    }
    .btn.primary:hover{transform: translateY(-2px)}
    .btn.ghost{
      color:#fff;
      background:rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    }
    .btn.ghost:hover{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.14)}

    /* About / Tools grid */
    .grid-2{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap:30px;
    }
    .card{
      background:var(--card);
      border:1px solid var(--border);
      box-shadow:var(--shadow);
      border-radius:var(--radius);
      padding:40px;
    }
    .card h3{
      font-size:26px;
      margin-bottom:18px;
      color:var(--main);
    }
    .card li{
      margin-bottom:12px;
      font-size:16px;
    }
    .keyword-wrap{
      display:flex;
      flex-wrap:wrap;
      gap:10px;
    }
    .keyword{
      padding:10px 14px;
      border-radius:999px;
      background:var(--main);
      color:#fff;
      font-weight:800;
      font-size:14px;
    }

    /* Career */
    section.career{background:var(--gray)}
    .timeline{
      display:flex;
      flex-direction:column;
      gap:18px;
    }
    .timeline-item{
      background:#fff;
      border:1px solid var(--border);
      border-left:6px solid var(--main);
      border-radius:22px;
      padding:30px;
      box-shadow:0 6px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
    }
    .timeline-item h3{
      font-size:22px;
      margin-bottom:12px;
      color:var(--main);
    }

    /* Project */
    section.project{
      background:#0a0a0a;
      color:#fff;
      position:relative;
      overflow:hidden;
    }
    section.project .section-title{color:#fff}
    .quote{
      margin:40px 0;
      font-size:32px;
      font-weight:900;
      line-height:1.4;
    }
    .project-card{
      background:rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
      border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.10);
      border-radius:26px;
      padding:36px;
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    }

    /* Footer */
    footer.footer{
      padding:80px 0;
      background:var(--main);
      color:#fff;
      text-align:center;
    }
    footer.footer h2{
      font-size:42px;
      font-weight:900;
      margin-bottom:12px;
    }

    /* Responsive */
    @media (max-width: 960px){
      .hero h1{font-size:48px}
      .grid-2{grid-template-columns:1fr}
      .section-title{font-size:34px}
      section{padding:90px 0}
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="topbar">
    <div class="inner">
      <div class="brand">KIM MINJI</div>
      <nav class="nav">
        <a href="#about">About</a>
        <a href="#experience">Experience</a>
        <a href="#project">Project</a>
        <a href="#tools">Tools</a>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </div>

  <header class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>
        끊이지 않는 호기심을<br />
        결과물로 증명합니다.
      </h1>
      <p>
        방송국, 신문사를 거쳐 현재는 AI와 실사 영화를 제작하고 있습니다.<br />
        사람들의 이야기를 더 깊게 연결하는 콘텐츠를 만듭니다.
      </p>
      <div class="cta-row">
        <a class="btn primary" href="mailto:maymay0518@naver.com">이메일로 연락하기</a>
        <a class="btn ghost" href="#about">포트폴리오 읽어보기 ↓</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main>
    <section id="about">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">ABOUT ME</h2>
        <p class="section-desc">사회학과 영화, AI 기술을 융합하여 새로운 스토리텔링의 가능성을 탐구합니다.</p>
        <div class="grid-2">
          <div class="card">
            <h3>Focus</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>한양대학교 사회학 & 연극영화학</li>
