              <li>콘텐츠 브랜딩 & 마케팅</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <h3>Keywords</h3>
            <div class="keyword-wrap">
              <span class="keyword">기획력</span>
              <span class="keyword">AI 기술 활용</span>
              <span class="keyword">스토리텔링</span>
